title: Ep 2689 - The Great Depression
shortDesc: Everyone is tensed in Gokuldham society regarding Popatlal's condition. Hathi tells Komal that if this is how it goes, Popatlal will go into depression where a person won't even feel like eating. Everyone decides to cheer up Popatlal.

title: Ep 2690 - Popatlals Despair
shortDesc: Champaklal tries to help Popatlal get out of depression but Popatlal doesn't see light at the end of the tunnel. Jethalal and Taarak Mehta decide to make Popatlal happy by gifting him a brand new phone but this plan also fails.

title: Ep 2691 - Happy Holi
shortDesc: The Gokuldham society members are worried about Popatlal. The society members are shocked seeing Popatlal, who arrives for the pooja covering his mouth.

title: Ep 2692 - The Message
shortDesc: The Gokuldham society members are celebrating Holi with fervour. Tappu notices that Popatlal hasn't come out of his house. The society members meet Popatlal and try to convince him to play Holi.

title: Ep 2693 - A Strange Message
shortDesc: Popatlal recieves a strange message from a stranger. Taarak plays the message on his laptop on which there appears a strange man with a message for all of them saying that they recieve a free ticket to Singapore. Who is this strange man?

title: Ep 2694 - The Emergency Meeting
shortDesc: Bhide and Jethalal are reassured that the Singapore trip is fully financed. Bhide calls for an emergency meeting to discuss whether Gokuldham society members should go to Singapore.

title: Ep 2695 - Singapore Confirmation
shortDesc: The members of Gokuldham manage to make Popatlal agree for the trip to Singapore. The dates of the trip though causes various problems to each of the families for several members. WIll they manage to go to Singapore, stay tuned to find out.

title: Ep 2696 - Gokuldham To Singapore
shortDesc: All the ladies help Popatlal for packing his stuff for which he is very obliged. Bhide gets a call from Thomas cook informing them not to book a cab to reach the airport as they have special arrangements for them. Stay tuned for more.

title: Ep 2697 - Jetha Rides To Sentosa
shortDesc: Gokuldham is finally in Singapore. They ride to the hotel and they loved the place, as the hotel executives make them feel at home. Jetha decides to go visit Sentosa and rides a bike with his father. The ride is surely exciting!

title: Ep 2698 - Gokuldham Is Finally In Singapore
shortDesc: Gokuldham is finally in Singapore. The whole Gokuldham is planning to explore the Singapore city, but Jethalal got confused while seeing Singapore's map, How Jethalal will manage in Singapore. To know more keep watching!

title: Ep 2699 - Everyone Enjoys The Amusement Park
shortDesc: Jethalal has sweet words with Babita on a giant wheel ride. Others enjoy the amusement park unknown of the fact that they are being spyed on. Who is the Spy, stay tuned to find out.

title: Ep 2700 - Bungee Jumping
shortDesc: After Babita asks about the best place in Santosa, Jehtalal finds out about it from a local who sugests Bungee Jumping to Jethalal. An unaware Jethalal takes everyone for the event but when he sees what actually it is, he is scared to death.

title: Ep 2701 - Iyer Mocks Jethalal
shortDesc: Everyone is enjoying the trip and gathers around, Babita goes and speaks to Iyer and Jethalal interrupts in between. Babita tells Iyer that he would have loved Bungee jumping with Jethalal if he would have been here, to which Iyer doesn't believe.

title: Ep 2702 - Gardens By The Bay
shortDesc: The next trip for Jetrhalal and his gang is Gardens By The Bay. They all are extremely excited to discover the different gardens all around. Taarak starts reciting poems and impresses Anjali. Do they know that their movements are being watched?

title: Ep 2703 - Gokuldham Explores The City Of Singapore
shortDesc: In this episode, the people of Gokuldham went to explore whole Singapore city, All are very excited to see Singapore.
